Baiklah. Baiklah!

763
00:46:41,013 --> 00:46:41,680
Siap!

764
00:46:42,014 --> 00:46:42,648
Ambil posisi!

765
00:46:42,981 --> 00:46:44,016
Mulai!

766
00:46:46,151 --> 00:46:47,186
Tangkap dia!

767
00:46:49,555 --> 00:46:50,556
Maaf.

768
00:46:51,423 --> 00:46:52,424
Tolong aku!

769
00:46:52,558 --> 00:46:53,358
Tarik!

770
00:46:53,492 --> 00:46:54,493
Oh, tidak! Tolong, siapa saja!

771
00:46:55,260 --> 00:46:56,295
Mundur! Mundur!

772
00:47:01,300 --> 00:47:02,334
Mundur!

773
00:47:07,706 --> 00:47:09,575
-Tolong aku! Singkirkan mereka!
