774
00:47:11,310 --> 00:47:12,311
Cepat!

775
00:47:14,680 --> 00:47:16,148
Tutup! Tutup!

776
00:47:16,281 --> 00:47:17,316
Sudah dapat semuanya?!

777
00:47:19,651 --> 00:47:20,619
Buka ikatanku!

778
00:47:20,752 --> 00:47:22,421
Aku membayangkan
