780
00:47:34,600 --> 00:47:36,068
Tidak, tidak, tidak!

781
00:47:36,201 --> 00:47:38,370
Kita harus pergi dari sini!
Kita harus ke ruang bawah tanah!

782
00:47:38,503 --> 00:47:40,272
-Terkunci.
-Sudah kubuka!

783
00:47:41,707 --> 00:47:43,175
Itu namanya masuk tanpa izin!

784
00:47:45,277 --> 00:47:47,212
Awas perangkap beruang!

785
00:47:50,749 --> 00:47:52,117
Kenapa kau taruh di sini?!

786
00:47:52,284 --> 00:47:53,752
Ayo! Cepat! Ayo!

787
00:48:06,331 --> 00:48:08,133
Cepat. Ayo.

788
00:48:09,601 --> 00:48:10,669
-Kunci pintunya!
-Baik.

789
00:48:10,802 --> 00:48:12,037
Kunci pintunya!

790
00:48:14,473 --> 00:48:17,476
Kenapa kau tidak menulis kisah tentang
