00:58:02,694 --> 00:58:03,728
-Tidak, itu adil.
-Sudahlah.

928
00:58:03,862 --> 00:58:04,662
Kalian sama-sama benar...

929
00:58:04,796 --> 00:58:05,797
...tapi kita harus terus jalan
sambil kalian bertengkar.

930
00:58:07,098 --> 00:58:09,300
Menyelinap tengah malam
dengan anak aneh.

931
00:58:09,634 --> 00:58:10,635
Sulit dipercaya.

932
00:58:10,768 --> 00:58:11,903
Tutup mulutmu.

933
00:58:16,107 --> 00:58:17,142
Oh, hei.

934
00:58:17,275 --> 00:58:19,177
-Boleh pinjam satu dolar?
