Oh! Oh. Terlalu jauh.

1407
01:32:35,431 --> 01:32:36,699
Dapat.

1408
01:32:50,012 --> 01:32:51,047
Halo.

1409
01:32:51,981 --> 01:32:54,450
Nama saya Pak R. L. Stine...

1410
01:32:54,784 --> 01:32:56,319
...dan saya
guru bahasa Inggris baru kalian...

1411
01:32:56,452 --> 01:32:58,054
...karena Tn. Boyd masih...

1412
01:32:58,187 --> 01:33:01,190
...dalam masa pemulihan
dari cedera yang dia dapat...

1413
01:33:01,390 --> 01:33:04,460
...dalam serangan serangga mutan.

1414
01:33:08,464 --> 01:33:10,733
Nah, setiap kisah
yang pernah diceritakan...

1415
01:33:10,866 --> 01:33:15,004
...dapat dibagi menjadi tiga bagian:

1416
01:33:15,137 --> 01:33:16,472
Permulaan...

1417
01:33:17,073 --> 01:33:18,341
...pertengahan...

1418
01:33:19,809 --> 01:33:21,043
...dan kejutan.

1419
01:33:23,145 --> 01:33:25,281
-Halo, Tn. Stine.
-Halo, Tn. Black.

1420
01:33:27,149 --> 01:33:29,418
-Siapa itu?
-Guru drama yang baru.

1421
01:33:33,489 --> 01:33:35,791
-Boleh bertanya sesuatu?
-Tentu.

1422
01:33:39,061 --> 01:33:40,062
Kau merindukan dia?

1423
01:33:40,196 --> 01:33:42,498
Aku memikirkannya setiap hari.

1424
01:33:43,099 --> 01:33:45,334
Tapi dia akan selalu di sini...

1425
01:33:46,035 --> 01:33:47,436
...dan di sana...

1426
01:33:48,204 --> 01:33:49,972
...dan di sini...

1427
01:33:50,106 --> 01:33:51,240
...dan di sini.

1428
01:33:52,508 --> 01:33:54,243
Dan juga di sana.

1429
01:34:03,452 --> 01:34:06,422
Mungkin aku menulis satu buku lagi.

1430
01:34:15,364 --> 01:34:16,399
Hannah.

1431
01:34:20,036 --> 01:34:21,804
Kau nyata?

1432
01:34:22,204 --> 01:34:23,205
Kau kembali?

1433
01:34:23,339 --> 01:34:25,141
Harus. Kau berutang dansa denganku.

